# Mobile — copy to .env only when you need to override the API URL.
# In dev, the app usually auto-detects your machine IP from the Expo dev server.

# Physical device on same Wi‑Fi as your PC (replace with your LAN IP):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.71:5001

# Emulator defaults are handled in lib/env.ts (e.g. Android → 10.0.2.2).
# After editing, restart Expo: npm start  (or: npx expo start -c)
